{"tid":448570,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港房屋問題，為左香港好，入來講下意見","createTime":"2017-10-26T10:30:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-25T21:30:25.000Z","uid":13969,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e8c0c94376c41fe4db45ead0126c6a038a491b00","tid":448570,"uid":13969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T10:30:32.000Z","msg":"文有少少長<br />\n點儲錢都係買唔起樓咖啦<br />\n儲錢買樓做樓奴不如租屋<br />\nd樓咁貴根本係因為大陸人炒樓<br />\n呢d我都明<br />\n但我地香港人都存在一個好大既問題<br />\n就係公屋<br />\n我知道連登仔都有唔少人住緊公屋<br />\n但我針對既唔係你地<br />\n而係公屋根本唔應該存在<br />\n點解？<br />\n公屋既濫用<br />\n缺點<br />\n係人都知<br />\n甚至有d公屋仲靚過居屋<br />\n有無搞撚錯？<br />\n但係根本無可能一刀切<br />\n我既建議係慢慢減少起公屋<br />\n轉做起多d居屋<br />\n學新加坡咁<br />\n用成本價賣比香港居民<br />\n一來大家會更有心去儲錢<br />\n如果唔係根本無人會去儲錢買私人樓<br />\n屌你老母<br />\n儲到夠<br />\n人都變老<br />\n二來，政府多左既錢可以起d更靚既居屋<br />\n香港屌你都無地<br />\n仲起相對質素較低既樓？<br />\n唔係針對住公屋既大家<br />\n但富戶住公屋<br />\n屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n支持既話就留下言<br />\n唔好比個負皮走左去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de57bbd58bf6fded2ec166ac558c19083be03577","tid":448570,"uid":13969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T10:30:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea89170756014b25e5ba0eb1d0555e47c7de4d8d","tid":448570,"uid":13969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T10:31:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7b9630a7bdf45c4149d78f76b0f17321bd6c458","tid":448570,"uid":19978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T10:31:23.000Z","msg":"洗唔洗開兩個"},{"pid":"2694df40f1eac66f85ebedea0e3a9f746160de12","tid":448570,"uid":13969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T10:31:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b167a1dd5648ce7d77bb305d9f2fcfbca599687a","tid":448570,"uid":13969,"like":0